---
description: Build, format, and test verification before commits
globs: ["**/*"]
alwaysApply: true
---

Before suggesting any commit:
1. Run `npm run lint` to verify formatting (Prettier check)
2. Run `npm run typecheck`, `npm run build`, and `npm run test`
3. Do not bypass pre-commit hooks
4. If any step fails, fix the issue before proceeding

These steps match `pr.verifyCommands` in `devx.config.mjs`.
